public class TimePickerDialog
extends AlertDialog
implements DialogInterface.OnClickListener, TimePicker.OnTimeChangedListener

A dialog that prompts the user for the time of day using a TimePicker.

嵌套类摘要
static interface TimePickerDialog.OnTimeSetListener
          The callback interface used to indicate the user is done filling in the time (they clicked on the 'Set' button).

onSaveInstanceState

public Bundle onSaveInstanceState()
从类 Dialog 复制的描述
Saves the state of the dialog into a bundle. The default implementation saves the state of its view hierarchy, so you'll likely want to call through to super if you override this to save additional state.

覆盖：
类 Dialog 中的 onSaveInstanceState
返回：
A bundle with the state of the dialog.

onRestoreInstanceState

public void onRestoreInstanceState(Bundle savedInstanceState)
从类 Dialog 复制的描述
Restore the state of the dialog from a previously saved bundle. The default implementation restores the state of the dialog's view hierarchy that was saved in the default implementation of Dialog.onSaveInstanceState(), so be sure to call through to super when overriding unless you want to do all restoring of state yourself.

覆盖：
类 Dialog 中的 onRestoreInstanceState
参数：
savedInstanceState - The state of the dialog previously saved by Dialog.onSaveInstanceState().
